channel.description: IN HONOR OF BILLY MAYS, WE SHOULD ALL TAKE THE TIME TO MEMORIALIZE HIS DEATH, AND TO REMEMBER HIM. SO, IN HONOR OF BILLY MAYS, PLEASE REMEMBER TO COMMUNICATE IN ALL CAPS ON EVERY JULY 20TH FROM NOW ON.
